Usage: analyze_paths_by_critical_false_path [-help]
                                            [-critical_false_paths {false_path_only exclude_false_path}]
                                            [-master <string>]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-critical_false_paths {false_path_only exclude_false_path}
                     # Specifies which paths to analyze. Default :
                     # false_path_only. (enum, optional)
-master <string>     # Specifies that the analysis should be performed only for
                     # the specified master category. (string, optional)